WEBVTT

00:02.222 --> 00:04.390
We are being watched.

00:04.392 --> 00:07.060
The government
has a secret system,

00:07.062 --> 00:11.263
a machine that spies on you
every hour of every day.

00:11.265 --> 00:13.466
I designed the machine
to detect acts of terror,

00:13.468 --> 00:15.033
but it sees everything,

00:15.035 --> 00:18.036
violent crimes involving
ordinary people.

00:18.038 --> 00:20.773
The government considers
these people irrelevant.

00:20.775 --> 00:22.741
We don't.

00:22.743 --> 00:27.279
Hunted by the authorities,
we work in secret.

00:27.281 --> 00:31.749
You will never find us,
but victim or perpetrator,

00:31.751 --> 00:34.686
if your number's up,
we'll find you.

